  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK517">
<l>itaṉai yitaṉā livaṉmuṭikku meṉṟāyn</l>
<l>tataṉai yavaṉkaṇ viṭal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>After having considered, "this man can accomplish this, by these means", let (the king) leave with him the discharge of that duty.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
